OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,FDrivers are suffering from "unfairly
OL,8,Fhigh margins" on fuel sales, a Cabinet
OL,9,Fminister has been warned.
OL,11,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,12,F(CMA) must be given the power to take
OL,13,F"meaningful action" against companies
OL,14,Fcharging too much for petrol and
OL,15,Fdiesel, according to a letter from the
OL,16,FRAC to Energy Secretary Claire
OL,17,FCoutinho.
