OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,FThe average retailer margin ` the
OL,8,Fdifference between the amount they pay
OL,9,Ffor fuel and the pump price ` has been
OL,10,Fabove 18p per litre for diesel since
OL,11,FMay 7 and is nearly 12p per litre for
OL,12,Fpetrol, RAC head of policy Simon
OL,13,FWilliams wrote.
OL,15,FThe long-term average for both fuels
OL,16,Fis 8p.
OL,18,FMargins have risen in recent days on
OL,19,Fthe back of wholesale costs reducing
OL,20,Fdue to a drop in oil prices.
