OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,FThe RAC believes if retailers charged
OL,8,F"fairer" margins, the average price of
OL,9,Fa litre of petrol and diesel would be
OL,10,Faround 145p, down from the current
OL,11,Fprices of 150p per litre for petrol
OL,12,Fand 157p per litre for diesel.
OL,14,FMr Williams wrote: "The RAC recognises
OL,15,Fthat retailers, along with all
OL,16,Fbusinesses, have been affected by high
OL,17,Flevels of inflation, but we feel that
OL,18,Fcurrent margins are extremely unfair
OL,19,Fon drivers struggling to get by in the
OL,20,Fcost-of-living crisis.
