OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,F"In addition, having tracked fuel
OL,8,Fprices against the Consumer Prices
OL,9,FIndex, we can see there is a clear
OL,10,Flink between the two, meaning unfairly
OL,11,Fhigh margins are making inflation
OL,12,Fhigher than it should be."
OL,14,FHe went on: "Even though there has
OL,15,Fnever been more fuel price data
OL,16,Fpublicly available, the issue of
OL,17,Fexcessively high retailer margins
OL,18,Fpersists.
