OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,F"The RAC believes this will only be
OL,8,Fimproved if the CMA as the price
OL,9,Fmonitoring body is able to take
OL,10,Fmeaningful action against retailers
OL,11,Fwhose margins appear unreasonable when
OL,12,Flooked at alongside the price of
OL,13,Fwholesale fuel."
OL,15,FFourteen of the biggest fuel retailers
OL,16,Fare voluntarily sharing daily price
OL,17,Fdata through a CMA scheme.
OL,19,FThe Government has proposed a
OL,20,Fmandatory Pump Watch fuel price
OL,21,Ftransparency programme.
