OL,8,FNet Zero spokesperson said: "The
OL,9,FEnergy Secretary has been clear that
OL,10,Fretailers who fail to pass on savings
OL,11,Fto drivers at the pumps will be held
OL,12,Fto account.
OL,14,F"We are already giving the CMA tough
OL,15,Fnew powers to force retailers to come
OL,16,Fclean on their prices and call out any
OL,17,Frip-off charges.
