OL,3,CDrivers hit by retailers making
OL,4,C'unfairly high margins' on fuel,
OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,F"Drivers deserve to know they are
OL,8,Fgetting a fair price for fuel and our
OL,9,FPumpWatch scheme will do just that,
OL,10,Fhelping them to find the best deal."
OL,12,FGordon Balmer, executive director of
OL,13,Fthe Petrol Retailers' Association,
OL,14,Fwhich represents independent fuel
OL,15,Fsellers, said: "Petrol retailers
OL,16,Fcontinue to offer motorists the best
OL,17,Fdeals possible while wrestling with
OL,18,Fskyrocketing increases to their fixed
OL,19,Fcosts.
