OL,5,Cminister warned
OL,7,F"Retailers are having to contend with
OL,8,Frecord levels of theft as well as
OL,9,Fincreases in business rates, energy
OL,10,Fbills and the National Minimum Wage.
OL,12,F"Our members are committed to keeping
OL,13,Fpump prices as low as possible for
OL,14,Ftheir customers but they are not
OL,15,Fimmune to the impact of geopolitical
OL,16,Fevents outside of their control.
